    <entry valign="top" align="left">Amide</entry>
    <entry valign="top" align="left"><media class="unnumbered" alt="The structure of an amide where an R group and an amino groups are connected to a carbonyl carbon."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/OChem_21_01_009d.jpg"/></media></entry>
